<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pre-Quote Assessment — St. Anne Center</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: #111009; color: #F4EFE0; min-height: 100vh; }

/* HEADER */
.site-header { background: #111009; border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2519; padding: 16px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
.logo-circle { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; background: #B8922A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: ‘Playfair Display’, serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111009; flex-shrink: 0; }
.header-text { flex: 1; }
.header-company { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #7A7260; }
.header-doc { font-size: 0.68rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #B8922A; margin-top: 2px; }
.gold-bar { height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #B8922A, #D4AC48, #B8922A); }

/* HERO */
.hero { padding: 24px 20px 0; }
.hero-title { font-family: ‘Playfair Display’, serif; font-size: 1.9rem; color: #F4EFE0; line-height: 1.2; }
.hero-sub { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #7A7260; margin-top: 6px; }
.hero-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 14px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2519; }
.chip { background: #1C1A12; border: 1px solid #3A3520; border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #D4AC48; }

/* TABS */
.tabs { display: flex; overflow-x: auto; border-bottom: 2px solid #2A2519; background: #111009; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; scrollbar-width: none; }
.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.tab { padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; color: #7A7260; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -2px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.tab.active { color: #D4AC48; border-bottom-color: #B8922A; }

/* PANELS */
.panel { display: none; padding: 24px 20px 48px; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
.panel.active { display: block; }

/* SHARED CONTENT STYLES */
.section-title { font-family: ‘Playfair Display’, serif; font-size: 1.3rem; color: #F4EFE0; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2519; }
.info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.info-item label { display: block; font-size: 0.65rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #6B5318; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.info-item .val { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #F4EFE0; }
.summary-box { background: #1C1A12; border-left: 3px solid #B8922A; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; padding: 14px 16px; font-size: 0.84rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #D4AC48; margin-bottom: 20px; }

/* SCOPE LIST */
.scope-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
.scope-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2519; align-items: flex-start; }
.scope-num { font-family: ‘Playfair Display’, serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #B8922A; font-weight: 700; min-width: 24px; line-height: 1; }
.scope-text h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: #F4EFE0; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.scope-text p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7A7260; line-height: 1.55; }
.tag { display: inline-block; border-radius: 3px; padding: 1px 6px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-left: 6px; }
.tag-warn { background: rgba(184,146,42,0.2); color: #D4AC48; }
.tag-bad { background: rgba(192,57,43,0.2); color: #E74C3C; }
.tag-good { background: rgba(39,174,96,0.2); color: #27AE60; }

/* MATERIALS TABLE */
.mat-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.81rem; margin-top: 16px; }
.mat-table th { text-align: left; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 0.67rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #B8922A; border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2519; }
.mat-table th.r { text-align: right; }
.mat-table td { padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1C1A12; color: #D4AC48; vertical-align: top; }
.mat-table td.label { color: #F4EFE0; }
.mat-table td.r { text-align: right; font-family: monospace; }
.mat-table .sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #7A7260; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
.mat-table .total td { border-top: 1px solid #B8922A; font-weight: 700; color: #D4AC48; }
.note-box { background: #1C1A12; border: 1px solid #2A2519; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7A7260; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; margin-top: 16px; }

/* PHOTOS */
.photo-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 16px; }
.photo-card { border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; aspect-ratio: 16/10; background: #1C1A12; }
.photo-card img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
.photo-overlay { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(17,16,9,0.9)); padding: 20px 12px 10px; }
.photo-overlay .elev { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; color: #D4AC48; }
.photo-overlay .dims { font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(212,172,72,0.65); margin-top: 2px; }

/* NOTES */
.note-item { background: #1C1A12; border-radius: 6px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-left: 3px solid #B8922A; }
.note-item h4 { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: #D4AC48; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.note-item p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7A7260; line-height: 1.6; }

@media (max-width: 480px) {
.info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.photo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.hero-title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="gold-bar"></div>
<div class="site-header">
  <div class="logo-circle">M&amp;P</div>
  <div class="header-text">
    <div class="header-company">Meat &amp; Potatoes Carpentry LLC &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Waterford, WI</div>
    <div class="header-doc">Pre-Quote Assessment</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-title">St. Anne Center</div>
  <div class="hero-sub">2801 East Morgan Avenue &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Milwaukee, WI &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Dayo Akande, COO &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; (414) 552-1254</div>
  <div class="hero-chips">
    <span class="chip">LP SmartSide Lap Siding</span>
    <span class="chip">LP SmartSide Trim 1&times;4</span>
    <span class="chip">Soffit Enclosure</span>
    <span class="chip">Full Exterior &mdash; All 4 Elevations</span>
    <span class="chip">Remove &amp; Dispose Existing</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tabs">
  <div class="tab active" onclick="showTab('overview')">Overview</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('scope')">Scope</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('materials')">Materials</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('photos')">Photos</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="showTab('notes')">Notes</div>
</div>

<!-- OVERVIEW -->

<div class="panel active" id="tab-overview">
  <div class="section-title">Job Overview</div>
  <div class="info-grid">
    <div class="info-item"><label>Customer</label><div class="val">St. Anne Center</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Contact</label><div class="val">Dayo Akande &mdash; COO</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Address</label><div class="val">2801 East Morgan Avenue<br>Milwaukee, WI</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Phone</label><div class="val">(414) 552-1254</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Assessment Date</label><div class="val" id="adate"></div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Assessor</label><div class="val">Dan Cleveland<br>Meat &amp; Potatoes Carpentry LLC</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Project Area</label><div class="val">All 4 Elevations &mdash; Full Exterior</div></div>
    <div class="info-item"><label>Building</label><div class="val">37&prime; &times; 33&prime; footprint, 17&prime; walls<br>2-story storage building</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="summary-box">
    Removal and disposal of all existing siding and trim on all four elevations of the exterior storage building on property. Application of LP SmartSide lap siding and 1&times;4 trim boards throughout. Soffit enclosure to seal open eave cavities and eliminate bird infiltration. Building shows extensive rot and paint failure &mdash; particularly severe at the base of the west and south elevations.
  </div>
  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:8px;">Site Conditions</div>
  <div class="scope-list">
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Overall Exterior Condition <span class="tag tag-bad">Poor</span></h4>
        <p>Extensive deterioration on all four elevations. Paint failure and rot concentrated at the base of all walls. Most severe at west and south elevations where siding is actively separating from the structure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>East Elevation &mdash; Boarded Window <span class="tag tag-warn">Flagged</span></h4>
        <p>One upper-level window on the east elevation is boarded with plywood. Must be addressed regardless of broader window scope.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Roof &amp; Gutters <span class="tag tag-good">New 2023</span></h4>
        <p>Asphalt shingle roof and gutters replaced in 2023 and in good condition. Not in scope. All work will be performed with care to protect the existing roofline and gutter system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Bird Infiltration &mdash; Upper Eaves <span class="tag tag-warn">Active</span></h4>
        <p>Facility staff report birds gaining access through open ceiling joist cavities at the eave line. Soffit enclosure proposed as permanent solution.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SCOPE -->

<div class="panel" id="tab-scope">
  <div class="section-title">Scope of Work</div>
  <div class="scope-list">
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">1</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Remove &amp; Dispose &mdash; All Existing Siding</h4>
        <p>Full tear-off and disposal of all existing siding material on all four elevations. Existing material is deteriorated and not salvageable. Debris removed from site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">2</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Remove &amp; Dispose &mdash; All Existing Trim</h4>
        <p>Full removal and disposal of all existing trim including corner boards, band board, and all window and door casings on all four elevations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">3</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Inspect Sheathing &amp; Install House Wrap</h4>
        <p>Sheathing condition assessed after demo. Water-resistive barrier installed where missing or damaged. Substrate rot repairs scoped separately via change order as needed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">4</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Install LP SmartSide Lap Siding</h4>
        <p>7/16&rdquo; &times; 8&rdquo; &times; 16&prime; panels at 6&rdquo; exposure throughout all four elevations. ~370 pieces including 10% waste.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">5</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Install LP SmartSide 1&times;4 Trim Boards</h4>
        <p>Corner boards at all four corners, horizontal band board at floor-line transition, and casings at all window and door openings. ~38 boards / 527 LF including waste.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">6</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Install Soffit Enclosure &mdash; Bird Infiltration Solution</h4>
        <p>Soffit material installed along full eave perimeter to permanently close off open joist bays and seal structure against bird entry. Material and footage TBD &mdash; measure on site. Performed concurrently with siding scope.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">*</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Entry Doors &mdash; TBD <span class="tag tag-warn">Discuss</span></h4>
        <p>Multiple entry doors in poor condition. Once new siding is in place, doors will be visually prominent. Replacement or TLC to be discussed with ownership before quote is finalized.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scope-row">
      <div class="scope-num">*</div>
      <div class="scope-text">
        <h4>Windows &mdash; Not in Scope / Return Visit <span class="tag tag-warn">Optional</span></h4>
        <p>Windows not measured at this visit. If replacement desired, return visit required. Ballpark pricing available upon request.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- MATERIALS -->

<div class="panel" id="tab-materials">
  <div class="section-title">Material Takeoff</div>
  <table class="mat-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Material</th><th class="r">Qty</th><th>Notes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">LP SmartSide Lap Siding<span class="sub">7/16&rdquo; &times; 8&rdquo; &times; 16&prime;</span></td>
        <td class="r">~370 pcs</td>
        <td>2,008 SF net area &divide; 6 SF per piece + 10% waste</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">LP SmartSide Trim Boards<span class="sub">1&times;4 &times; 16&prime;</span></td>
        <td class="r">~38 boards</td>
        <td>527 LF total + 15% waste</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">Soffit Material<span class="sub">TBD &mdash; LP or Aluminum</span></td>
        <td class="r">TBD</td>
        <td>Measure eave perimeter on site</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">House Wrap (WRB)<span class="sub">If required</span></td>
        <td class="r">TBD</td>
        <td>Confirm at demo</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">LP-Approved Fasteners</td>
        <td class="r">TBD</td>
        <td>Per LP spec sheet</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">Color-Matched Caulk</td>
        <td class="r">TBD</td>
        <td>Recommended at all seams</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:28px;">Wall Area Breakdown</div>
  <table class="mat-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Elevation</th><th>Dimensions</th><th class="r">Gross SF</th><th class="r">Deduct</th><th class="r">Net SF</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="label">North</td><td>37&prime; &times; 17&prime;</td><td class="r">629</td><td class="r">90</td><td class="r">539</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">East</td><td>33&prime; &times; 17&prime;</td><td class="r">561</td><td class="r">120</td><td class="r">441</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">South</td><td>37&prime; &times; 17&prime;</td><td class="r">629</td><td class="r">150</td><td class="r">479</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">West</td><td>33&prime; &times; 17&prime;</td><td class="r">561</td><td class="r">12</td><td class="r">549</td></tr>
      <tr class="total"><td class="label"><strong>Total</strong></td><td></td><td class="r">2,380</td><td class="r">372</td><td class="r"><strong>2,008</strong></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:28px;">Trim Linear Footage</div>
  <table class="mat-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Trim Location</th><th>Description</th><th class="r">LF</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="label">Corner Boards</td><td>4 corners &times; 2 boards &times; 17&prime;</td><td class="r">136</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">Band Board</td><td>Horizontal break &mdash; all 4 sides</td><td class="r">140</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">Window Casings</td><td>~10 windows avg 14 LF each</td><td class="r">140</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">Overhead Door Casings</td><td>3 doors &times; ~17 LF</td><td class="r">51</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="label">Entry Door Casings</td><td>3 doors &times; ~20 LF</td><td class="r">60</td></tr>
      <tr class="total"><td class="label"><strong>Total Trim LF</strong></td><td></td><td class="r"><strong>527</strong></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- PHOTOS -->

<div class="panel" id="tab-photos">
  <div class="section-title">Site Photos</div>
  <div class="photo-grid">
    <div class="photo-card">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="North Elevation">
      <div class="photo-overlay">
        <div class="elev">North Elevation</div>
        <div class="dims">37&prime; wide &times; 17&prime; tall</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-card">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="East Elevation">
      <div class="photo-overlay">
        <div class="elev">East Elevation</div>
        <div class="dims">33&prime; wide &times; 17&prime; tall &mdash; severe base rot</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-card">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="South Elevation">
      <div class="photo-overlay">
        <div class="elev">South Elevation</div>
        <div class="dims">37&prime; wide &times; 17&prime; tall &mdash; rot at base</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-card">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="West Elevation">
      <div class="photo-overlay">
        <div class="elev">West Elevation</div>
        <div class="dims">33&prime; wide &times; 17&prime; tall &mdash; worst damage</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NOTES -->

<div class="panel" id="tab-notes">
  <div class="section-title">Notes &amp; Next Steps</div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Substrate Contingency &mdash; Change Order Language</h4>
    <p>Full extent of rot into sheathing and framing cannot be determined until demolition begins. Contract should include a change order provision for substrate/framing repairs discovered during demo &mdash; particularly at the base of the west and south elevations where separation is visible.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Siding Color &amp; Finish Selection Needed</h4>
    <p>LP SmartSide color and finish to be confirmed by ownership before material order can be placed.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Soffit Measurement Required</h4>
    <p>Eave perimeter measurement and soffit product selection (LP SmartSide, aluminum, or vented panel) needed before soffit scope can be fully priced.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Entry Door Decision</h4>
    <p>Multiple entry doors are in rough condition. Determine with ownership whether replacement or refurbishment will be included in scope before quote is finalized.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Windows &mdash; Optional Return Visit</h4>
    <p>If window replacement is desired, a return visit for rough opening measurements is required. Ballpark pricing can be provided on request. Boarded east window must be addressed regardless.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="note-item">
    <h4>Disposal &amp; Site Logistics</h4>
    <p>Confirm dumpster placement, site access, and any facility-specific logistics with St. Anne Center facilities team before mobilization.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function showTab(id) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(function(t) { t.classList.remove('active'); });
    document.querySelectorAll('.panel').forEach(function(p) { p.classList.remove('active'); });
    document.getElementById('tab-' + id).classList.add('active');
    event.target.classList.add('active');
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
  }
  document.getElementById('adate').textContent = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' });
</script>

</body>
</html>
